message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted to meet your needs. This product comes with a range of advanced features and capabilities that promise to significantly enhance your experience. Considering its quality and functionality, we believe it's worth more than $15000. For this incredible opportunity, I am extending an exclusive offer to you at a price of $20000. This offer is valid for a limited time only, so please let me know if you're interested in securing this exceptional product.
